sequenceDiagram
  participant UWP as COMP-DEVICE-004 UWP DeviceConfiguration
  participant API as COMP-API-002 Backend /api/device
  participant IotSvc as COMP-INTEG-001 IotHubService
  participant IoTHub as Azure IoT Hub registry

  UWP->>UWP: Read EasClientDeviceInformation.Id
  UWP->>API: POST /api/device { id }
  Note over UWP,API: No authentication or authorization control found in inspected workspace
  API->>IotSvc: RegisterDevice(Device)
  IotSvc->>IoTHub: AddDeviceAsync(deviceId)
  alt Device already exists
    IoTHub-->>IotSvc: DeviceAlreadyExistsException
    IotSvc->>IoTHub: GetDeviceAsync(deviceId)
  end
  IoTHub-->>IotSvc: Device identity and symmetric key
  IotSvc-->>API: IoT Hub Device
  API-->>UWP: 201 JSON { deviceKey, deviceId }
  UWP->>UWP: Cache deviceKey in memory only
